{
  "stem": "5248.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he said-- well, actually he spoke that he was photographer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they let him go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then the next-- we were not allowed to leave city after 7 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Nevertheless, in the next few days, peasant woman came with pieces of clothing that leaves no doubt that they were all shot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was, of course, you could see that the pit was filled, fresh earth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But still, people had delusions that maybe some of them were taken somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, he was one of them, so--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till the next few days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have to get some water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the news repeated itself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, I think one week later, there came-- there came another transport of Gestapo And they took-- this time they took more people, I think 200 people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they just-- they took them just at random, from house to house, and--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they took all, all men at this time, and they-- actually very simple.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- my grandfather was taken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they just repeated the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people still believed that, that this-- [INAUDIBLE], was still naive about the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So very soon, many men from Dubno were gone, were shot, actually.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- and then we decided to move to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I don't know why, it always was thought that that would be a safer place than staying in Dubno, in Dubno.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But somebody help us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could not leave ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could not leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to stay where you are usually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a curfew at 7 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ghetto became later.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They let actually people still live in their places through the winter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And ghetto became in spring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to Lwow, which that was illusion.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
